        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Seamless.AI offers a free plan with a limited number of monthly credits. You can search for contacts, verify emails, and test the Chrome extension without paying anything. It's a genuine free tier, not just a trial that expires after 14 days.",
            "marks": []
          }
