      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Seamless.AI uses a real-time search engine rather than a static database, which means it verifies data at the moment you search. Users commonly report email accuracy rates above 90%, with bounce rates significantly lower than traditional data providers. The tool also marks confidence levels so you know how reliable each contact is.",
