            "text": "No, and it's not designed to. Seamless.AI is a prospecting and data enrichment tool that feeds into your CRM. It integrates natively with Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive, and others, pushing verified contact data directly into your pipeline. Think of it as the engine that fills your CRM with accurate, fresh leads.",
